                "invention-title": [
                    "Silicon wafer gettering treatment method, silicon wafer and silicon-based semiconductor physical device",
                    "一种硅片吸杂处理方法及硅片和硅基半导体物理器件"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides a silicon wafer gettering treatment method, a silicon wafer and a silicon-based semiconductor physical device, and the silicon wafer gettering treatment method comprises the following steps: depositing a silicide layer on the surface of the silicon wafer, the silicide layer being carbon and/or nitrogen-doped amorphous silicon containing phosphorus or boron or not containing phosphorus or boron; performing high-temperature treatment on the silicon wafer to form a diffusion layer on the surface of the silicon wafer; hydrotreating the surface of the silicon wafer; and etching treatment: sequentially removing the hydrogenation layer, the silicide layer and the diffusion layer on the surface of the silicon wafer. Carbon-containing and/or nitrogen-containing doped amorphous silicon is used as the source layer, carbon/nitrogen elements can be diffused into the silicon wafer through high-temperature treatment, during subsequent hydrotreating, the hydrogen concentration in the silicon wafer can be improved by utilizing the capturing effect of carbon/nitrogen atoms on hydrogen atoms, and the body life of the silicon wafer is remarkably prolonged by utilizing the passivation effect of hydrogen on defects, so that the yield of the silicon wafer is improved. And the performance of the silicon semiconductor device based on the low-temperature process is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种硅片吸杂处理方法及硅片和硅基半导体物理器件，硅片吸杂处理方法包括以下步骤：在硅片表面沉积硅化物层，所述硅化物层为碳和/或氮掺杂的含磷或硼或不含磷、硼的非晶硅；对硅片进行高温处理，在硅片表面形成扩散层；对硅片表面进行氢化处理；刻蚀处理，依次去除氢化层、硅化物层和硅片表面的扩散层。本发明以含碳和/或含氮的掺杂非晶硅作为源层，通过高温处理，碳/氮元素会扩散进去硅片内部，在后续氢化处理时，利用碳/氮原子对氢原子的捕获作用，可以提升硅片内部的氢浓度，利用氢对缺陷的钝化作用，从而显著提高硅片的体寿命，进而提升基于低温工艺的硅半导体器件的性能。"
                }
            ]
